    {
      "text": "Painter Momopie is a 1990 maze video game developed and published by Sigma Enterprises for the Game Boy. The player controls the witch Momopie, with the objective being to clean all the floors in a castle, and also to avoid and counter the foes that are in it. Various spells that Momopie acquires throughout the game help her in cleaning the castle faster, and/or are able to stop the enemies within it, though at the cost of MP.",
